item.title: Need helps with npc's
item.dc:creator: @Phaze_One Fuscate
item.description:
@Phaze_One wrote:

Add him to your models folder. Put the int’s that should have come with the model into class5.java. Save, compile. Open up your client and type in

add models

A whole bunch of things will show up and it will disconnect and reconnect you. Then spawn it. Simple.
